Package it.polimi.se2019.util

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    LocalModel
    The local model interface is used to build the model storage on top of it
    Message
    The interface message
    NetMsg
    Net msg class, this is different from the net message this one travels over the net directly
    Observer<T>
    This is a key part, the observer waits for an update by the observable
    RmiClientInterface
    The RmiClientInterface interface is the client interface that extends the Remote interface for RMI communitation.
    RmiServerInterface
    The RmiServerInterface is the server interface that extends the Remote interface and exposes two methods.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CommandConstants
    Those constants are used to set some conventional values for the params of the Conditions.
    DeserializerConstants
    Those constants are used to set some conventional values for the deserializer, all the fields of the json files have an entry here.
    ErrorResponse
    This class is basically a wrapper of the String class, this class was designed to have more functionality but due to lack of time they were never implemented.
    InternalMessage
    This class represents a set of commands.
    MessageParser
    Transform a Message in a List of PlayerActions using reflection so that the Controller can check/setUp them.
    NetMessage
    Net message class
    Observable<T>
    This is a key part, the observable is the baseline for the majority of our classes, provides the method used to communicate internally
    Request
    Request objects are used by the View to send data to the Controller.
    RequestParser
    The RequestParser class is used to parse a request message from the server, by parsing the internal message of a request.
    Response
    The Response class is the network object that is sent from server to client for any kind of notification and communitation.
    RuntimeTypeAdapterFactory<T>
    Adapts values whose runtime type may differ from their declaration type.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    Observer.CommunicationError
    The exception that notify if something is wrong
